  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Emergency Peace: Rapid Funds for Local Response</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will provide micro grants to volunteer District Peace Committees (DPCs) in over 30 districts of Somalia to support their reconciliation efforts. The project, by helping DPCs respond to conflict rapidly, will ensure early action to prevent escalation of disputes that may lead to violent conflict. DPCs already respond to issues related to gender-based violence, property disputes, and clan conflicts. They provide mediation, community dialogues, and conflict prevention activities.</narrative>
  </description>
